{"tid":1303780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中運動少少意見","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T12:21:11.000Z","uid":224136,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb15210dca9ea4f16959d69099afd6656cf713c2","tid":1303780,"uid":224136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"本人10分支持反送中運動，亦都親身支持各項大小活動，不過有少少意見，希望大家設計活動嘅時候可以對準少少。就係大家要留意活動嘅時候應該要一矢中的。例如近排針對TVB嘅活動，目的係要令到TVB重新去審視新聞部，踢走袁志偉改變新聞方針。所以個目的應該明確指出希望無線可以改變新聞方針，以持平角度報道新聞。唔係就咁鬧完就算。你要記得依度既影響力好大，你哋不停咁樣講嘢，會令到全港方向都有所改變<br />\n<br />\n我嘅意見係，所有嘅活動都要有具體嘅目標，令人哋容易記得，咁樣運動先至唔會偏離唔會比人哋有機會插你。<br />\n<br />\n以上係本人嘅小小意見，希望運動可以遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n香港加油。"},{"pid":"b76415e67054f499c81a36c7737b8c4b9f6ab11d","tid":1303780,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:19:39.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>NOW</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30</span></span><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=eed11808\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=2ee9a309\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n<strong>7.12</strong> - <ins>